  "I’ll log this concern about the shipping line as a ticket for KTC. Send it?": "Ilo-log ko ang concern na ’to tungkol sa shipping line bilang ticket para sa KTC. Ipadala?",
  "I’ll log this logistics / trucking concern as a ticket for KTC. Send it?": "Ilo-log ko ang logistics / trucking concern na ’to bilang ticket para sa KTC. Ipadala?",
  "I’ll log your complaint as a ticket so KTC customer service follows up. Send it?": "Ilo-log ko ang reklamo mo bilang ticket para may follow-up ang KTC customer service. Ipadala?",
  "I’ll pass your suggestion to KTC as a ticket. Send it?": "Ipapasa ko ang mungkahi mo sa KTC bilang ticket. Ipadala?",
  "Send to KTC": "Ipadala sa KTC",
  "Done — ticket #{ref} is open. KTC will reply in your Support tab; tap Open Support to see it.": "Ayos — bukas na ang ticket #{ref}. Sasagot ang KTC sa Support tab mo; i-tap ang Open Support para makita.",
  "I couldn’t create the ticket right now. You can reach KTC directly on the Support page, or try again.": "Hindi ko nagawa ang ticket ngayon. Pwede mong direktang i-contact ang KTC sa Support page, o subukan ulit.",
  "Please type a few words first.": "Magtype muna ng ilang salita.",
  "Hmm, I couldn’t check that right now. Want me to open a ticket so KTC can look?": "Hmm, hindi ko ma-check ngayon. Gusto mo bang mag-open ng ticket para tingnan ng KTC?",
  "I couldn’t find order {jo} on your account — check My Job Orders to confirm the number.": "Wala akong nakitang order na {jo} sa account mo — tingnan sa My Job Orders para ma-kumpirma ang number.",
  "Hmm, I couldn’t load your orders right now. You can open My Job Orders directly.": "Hmm, hindi ko ma-load ang orders mo ngayon. Pwede mong buksan nang diretso ang My Job Orders.",
  "Track a specific order": "Mag-track ng partikular na order",
