  "The live queue — submitted, processing, and on-hold orders. Tap to open the working queue. Most of the day-to-day lives there: process orders, confirm payments, record invoices.": "Ang live na queue — mga order na na-submit, pinoproseso, at naka-hold. I-tap para buksan ang working queue. Nandoon ang karamihan ng araw-araw na trabaho: i-process ang mga order, i-confirm ang mga payment, i-record ang mga invoice.",
  "The printed OR / Billing Invoice serial from the pad": "Ang naka-print na OR / Billing Invoice serial mula sa pad",
  "The Rate Calculator estimates your fees — pick services and container counts to see the estimated total, inclusive of VAT and fees.": "I-estimate ng Rate Calculator ang fees mo — pumili ng services at bilang ng container para makita ang estimated total, kasama na ang VAT at fees.",
  "This is the legal name verified against your ID. Changing it requires re-verification (you’ll re-upload an ID for an admin to review).": "Ito ang legal na pangalan na na-verify base sa ID mo. Kapag binago ito, kailangan ng re-verification (mag-u-upload ka ulit ng ID para i-review ng admin).",
